---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import pic3 from '../images/sub-1.jpg';
import pic4 from '../images/sub-2.jpg';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
  <section>
    <div>
      Ready to turn your event into an unforgettable celebration? Booking your
      360-photo booth with us at Yehovah entertainment is as easy as capturing
      the perfect shot. Contact us today to discuss your event details and let
      us tailor a photo booth experience our expectations. Are you excited to
      shoot your favorite gifs,boomerangs and videos through our unique
      expereince with an affordable pricing? Give us a call and we will help you
      out to make your event memorable anywhere, anytime.
    </div>
    <div>
      Embark on a journey where innovation meets celebration, and every photo
      tells a story - choose Yehovah Entertainment's 360 Photobooths for an
      event that transcends the ordinary. Step away from the conventional and
      embrace the extraordinary! Our 360- degree photobooths redefine event
      photography, capturing moments from every angle. The result? Mesmerizing,
      immersive memories that stand out in a world saturated with ordinary
      snapshots.
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="item">
        <div class="polaroid">
          <Image src={pic3} alt="sasasa" />
          <!-- <div class="caption">I Miss London</div> -->
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <div class="polaroid">
        <Image src={pic4} alt="sas" />
      </div>
  </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .wrapper {
  padding: 0 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}

.polaroid {
  background: #333;
  padding: 1rem;
  box-shadow: 0 0.2rem 1.2rem rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  
  
}
.polaroid > img{
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}
.caption {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 2em;
}
.item {
  width: 30%;
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 2rem;
  transform: scale(0.8, 0.8) rotate(6deg);
}

.polaroid:before {
    transform: rotate(6deg);
    height: 20%;
    width: 47%;
    bottom: 30px;
    right: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2.1rem 2rem rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}
</style>
